      "description": "Model is applicable to centrifugal blood pumps with impeller tip speeds between 3 m/s and 12 m/s, blood viscosity 0.0035–0.005 Pa·s, hematocrit 35–50%, and Reynolds numbers in the range 500–15000. Predictions outside these bounds require additional validation evidence. Geometry must conform to FDA generic pump topology within ±10% dimensional tolerance."
    },
